        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/edgy/mission_fox/scene_fox_contractcreation.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 9d630620-8593-4fc7-a3b5-b726370ebf3b).Image",
        "Description": "Your targets are those who lust for the thrill of chemicals and you must  punish them with irony. Theresia and Cornelius must be overdosed with chemicals twice and Michail must have his silver tounge and throat cut out with a provided axe. (The ICA combat axe is unlocked in mendoza mastery level 7, you must sicken Theresia and Cornelius via cocain bricks being chucked into the fans, brick 1 is in the 1st floor of the bicker place and brick 2 is in the safe in hirschmuller&apos;s office, code 1989.)",
